===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[brother]] or [[brother-in-law]] of someone’s [[parent]].
# {{figuratively}} A source of [[advice]], [[encouragement]], or [[help]].
# {{British|informal}} A [[pawnbroker]].
# {{context|Southern|_|US|colloquial}} A close male friend of the parents of a family.

